    <http://www.w3.org/2004/02/skos/core#prefLabel> "Nationale Zentralbanken außerhalb des Eurosystem: Българска народна банка, Česká národní banka, Danmarks Nationalbank, Hrvatska narodna banka, Magyar Nemzeti Bank, Narodowy Bank Polski, Banca Națională a României, Sveriges Riksbank, Bank of England"@de, "Εθνικές τράπεζες εκτός του Ευρωσυστήματος: Българска народна банка, Česká národní banka, Danmarks Nationalbank, Hrvatska narodna banka, Magyar Nemzeti Bank, Narodowy Bank Polski, Banca Națională a României, Sveriges Riksbank, Bank of England"@el, "Centralne banke držav članic zunaj evrosistema: Българска народна банка, Česká národní banka, Danmarks Nationalbank, Hrvatska narodna banka, Magyar Nemzeti Bank, Narodowy Bank Polski, Banca Națională a României, Sveriges Riksbank, Bank of England"@sl, "Nationale banker uden for Eurosystemet: Българска народна банка, Česká národní banka, Danmarks Nationalbank, Hrvatska narodna banka, Magyar Nemzeti Bank, Narodowy Bank Polski, Banca Națională a României, Sveriges Riksbank, Bank of England"@da, "Eurojärjestelmään kuulumattomat keskuspankit: Българска народна банка, Česká národní banka, Danmarks Nationalbank, Hrvatska narodna banka, Magyar Nemzeti Bank, Narodowy Bank Polski, Banca Națională a României, Sveriges Riksbank, Bank of England"@fi, "Bancos nacionales no pertenecientes al Eurosistema: Българска народна банка, Česká národní banka, Danmarks Nationalbank, Hrvatska narodna banka, Magyar Nemzeti Bank, Narodowy Bank Polski, Banca Națională a României, Sveriges Riksbank, Bank of England"@es, "Riiklikud pangad väljaspool eurosüsteemi: Българска народна банка, Česká národní banka, Danmarks Nationalbank, Hrvatska narodna banka, Magyar Nemzeti Bank, Narodowy Bank Polski, Banca Națională a României, Sveriges Riksbank, Bank of England"@et, "Nacionalne banke izvan Eurosustava: Българска народна банка, Česká národní banka, Danmarks Nationalbank, Hrvatska narodna banka, Magyar Nemzeti Bank, Narodowy Bank Polski, Banca Națională a României, Sveriges Riksbank, Bank of England"@hr, "Banek nazzjonali barra l-Eurosistema: Българска народна банка, Česká národní banka, Danmarks Nationalbank, Hrvatska narodna banka, Magyar Nemzeti Bank, Narodowy Bank Polski, Banca Națională a României, Sveriges Riksbank, Bank of England"@mt, "Národní banky mimo Eurosystém: Българска народна банка, Česká národní banka, Danmarks Nationalbank, Hrvatska narodna banka, Magyar Nemzeti Bank, Narodowy Bank Polski, Banca Națională a României, Sveriges Riksbank, Bank of England"@cs, "National banks outside the Eurosystem: Българска народна банка, Česká národní banka, Danmarks Nationalbank, Hrvatska narodna banka, Magyar Nemzeti Bank, Narodowy Bank Polski, Banca Națională a României, Sveriges Riksbank, Bank of England"@en, "Banche nazionali non appartenenti all’Eurosistema: Българска народна банка, Česká národní banka, Danmarks Nationalbank, Hrvatska narodna banka, Magyar Nemzeti Bank, Narodowy Bank Polski, Banca Națională a României, Sveriges Riksbank, Bank of England"@it, "Bancos nacionais não participantes no Eurosistema: Българска народна банка, Česká národní banka, Danmarks Nationalbank, Hrvatska narodna banka, Magyar Nemzeti Bank, Narodowy Bank Polski, Banca Națională a României, Sveriges Riksbank, Bank of England"@pt, "Nationella banker utanför Eurosystemet: Българска народна банка, Česká národní banka, Danmarks Nationalbank, Hrvatska narodna banka, Magyar Nemzeti Bank, Narodowy Bank Polski, Banca Națională a României, Sveriges Riksbank, Bank of England"@sv, "Национални банки извън Евросистемата: Българска народна банка, Česká národní banka, Danmarks Nationalbank, Hrvatska narodna banka, Magyar Nemzeti Bank, Narodowy Bank Polski, Banca Națională a României, Sveriges Riksbank, Bank of England"@bg, "Bainc náisiúnta lasmuigh den Eurochóras: Българска народна банка, Česká národní banka, Danmarks Nationalbank, Hrvatska narodna banka, Magyar Nemzeti Bank, Narodowy Bank Polski, Banca Națională a României, Sveriges Riksbank, Bank of England"@ga, "Národné banky, ktoré nepatria do Eurosystému: Българска народна банка, Česká národní banka, Danmarks Nationalbank, Hrvatska narodna banka, Magyar Nemzeti Bank, Narodowy Bank Polski, Banca Națională a României, Sveriges Riksbank, Bank of England"@sk, "Bănci naționale care nu fac parte din Eurosistem: Българска народна банка, Česká národní banka, Danmarks Nationalbank, Hrvatska narodna banka, Magyar Nemzeti Bank, Narodowy Bank Polski, Banca Națională a României, Sveriges Riksbank, Bank of England"@ro, "Valsts bankas ārpus Eurosistēmas: Българска народна банка, Česká národní banka, Danmarks Nationalbank, Hrvatska narodna banka, Magyar Nemzeti Bank, Narodowy Bank Polski, Banca Națională a României, Sveriges Riksbank, Bank of England"@lv, "Eurosistemai nepriklausantys nacionaliniai bankai: Българска народна банка, Česká národní banka, Danmarks Nationalbank, Hrvatska narodna banka, Magyar Nemzeti Bank, Narodowy Bank Polski, Banca Națională a României, Sveriges Riksbank, Bank of England"@lt, "Eurórendszeren kívüli nemzeti bankok: Българска народна банка, Česká národní banka, Danmarks Nationalbank, Hrvatska narodna banka, Magyar Nemzeti Bank, Narodowy Bank Polski, Banca Națională a României, Sveriges Riksbank, Bank of England"@hu, "Banques nationales n’appartenant pas à l’Eurosystème: Българска народна банка, Česká národní banka, Danmarks Nationalbank, Hrvatska narodna banka, Magyar Nemzeti Bank, Narodowy Bank Polski, Banca Națională a României, Sveriges Riksbank, Bank of England"@fr, "Banki krajowe poza Eurosystemem: Българска народна банка, Česká národní banka, Danmarks Nationalbank, Hrvatska narodna banka, Magyar Nemzeti Bank, Narodowy Bank Polski, Banca Națională a României, Sveriges Riksbank, Bank of England"@pl, "Nationale banken buiten het Eurosysteem: Българска народна банка, Česká národní banka, Danmarks Nationalbank, Hrvatska narodna banka, Magyar Nemzeti Bank, Narodowy Bank Polski, Banca Națională a României, Sveriges Riksbank, Bank of England"